description: This dataset aggregates and displays the number of New York State Medicaid enrollees by eligibility year and month within each NYS Economic Region;  health insurance plan information; and enrollee demographics.  For more information, check out http://www.health.ny.gov/health_care/medicaid/, or go to the "About" tab.
